docs.title: Spam
docs.text:
A spammer.

Parameters:

Name Type Description Default n int

How many times to spam.

required

Examples:

>>> from shiny_pyseed_demo.spam import Spam
>>> spammer = Spam(5)
>>> spammer.spam()
SPAM SPAM SPAM SPAM SPAM
